snippet.title: Taiko no Tatsujin: Rhythm Festival - DON DON Fitness: Dum Your Way to Fitness! Trailer
snippet.description:
／
Drum your way to Fitness!! ✨
＼

A completely new game mode, DON DON Fitness, is released for #TaikonoTatstujin: Rhythm Festival. Move your body to the groove of your favourite songs by hitting drum notes flying in and Drum Your Way to Fitness!

Learn More: https://bnent.asia/TnTRF
